Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌和最喜欢产生的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的推理和悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.30,0:00:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小兰一起去纽约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生在女影星身上的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.80,0:01:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上真的有上帝吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 天使从来没有对我微笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.20,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 是那个时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一也在的 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.60,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（事件篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.50,0:02:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 喂 小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.80,0:03:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.30,0:03:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰…小兰姐姐她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 烧得那么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和医院说一声 我们马上过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 警部 哪个医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨海大桥过去不是就有一家急救医院吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有我认识的医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上可以准备好床位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐警车过去不用十分钟就能到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去把车发动起来 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.30,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新一吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.20,0:04:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不甘心啊 又被你救了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是在我最痛苦的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能看穿我的心思一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很不甘心 但是好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.40,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Statue of Liberty
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本叫它自由女神像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在纽约被叫做Miss Liberty
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 为什么不把我叫起来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想从这座布鲁克林大桥上看曼哈顿的夜景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多都错过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.40,0:05:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你在飞机上不好好睡 所以现在才会困得睡着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了那种案件怎么可能还睡得着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和某位看穿了真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就满意地呼呼大睡的侦探不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要达到分析和推理的顶峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.30,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使花费一生也不够哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华生同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.50,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种全世界恋人都想来的恋爱圣地吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人嫉妒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是都怪老妈你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是明天才来纽约的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到洛杉矶马上又转机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为已经没指望的音乐剧的票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？音乐剧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.10,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.60,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最近这里很流行的Golden Apple啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 百老汇的魅影剧院 晚八点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.20,Default4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom：魅影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人期待呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你不觉得从刚才开始警车就变多了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 一定是因为那个杀人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人狂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.50,0:06:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是以年轻女子为目标的杀人狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是日裔男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.00,0:07:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个杀人狂只在午夜0点后才出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在那之前回旅馆的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会遇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不到六点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快七点了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是夏时制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 完全忘了还有夏时制这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从四月的第一个星期日开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前一个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好着急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这座桥到魅影剧院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车只要四十分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不到七点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间绰绰有余 不会迟到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和给我票的人约好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在开演前一个小时到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以带我们参观后台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈凭兴趣买的这辆英国小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对来不及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是你说的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会再慢慢欣赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美洲豹公司推出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆美洲豹E型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看它哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆车不是上个月刚修过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚拿回来不久吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的制造商看了以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又重新装备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,276马力的发动机做心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.40,0:09:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有在Le Mans比赛中获得优胜的轮轴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.10,0:09:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 会把巡逻车引来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 他们在反向车道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他们看到这优雅的车体时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就消失不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一和小兰能不能做一下那个姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的弯道可能有些困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.90,0:09:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小兰 稍微过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哦 怎么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.60,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一开始的时候会觉得害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要紧紧的抓住我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 没什么大不了的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫没有什么大不了的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好提前一个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 毫无问题的安全到达了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.30,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出示你的驾驶执照和入境许可证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your license and registration,please!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超速四十英里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40 miles over the speed limit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在扮演「紧急追捕令」的男主角吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing Dirty Harry?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我们有急事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh，we were in a hurry…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象在哪里见过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look familiar.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…你大概是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well，you might…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概是在某个案件中见过她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.47,0:11:33.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might have met her in some case.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because she works with us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是秘密进行调查的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's an undercover agent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.57,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子她好像把犯人跟丢了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.57,0:11:45.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have missed the criminal…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大叔是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉迪修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.40,0:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优作以前帮他们破案时认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽约市的警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉迪修·雷伍德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他妻子是日本人 所以他日语也是很棒的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了 拉迪修 可帮了大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 你谢错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 谢错人了是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.10,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要谢的话 就谢我怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.30,0:12:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.60,0:12:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要谢的话 就谢我怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.10,0:12:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我这位莎朗·温亚德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎…莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个警部是我的影迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.40,0:13:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等你的时候和他聊了一会儿天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候他的对讲机响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是一辆银色的车子用超常的速度向这里驶来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就穿上他的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,易容成了拉迪修警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.10,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件男士外套很贵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.30,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系吗 那么多人在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不会有问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经和大家说是在拍电影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我最喜欢莎朗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 妈妈啊 拜托你告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新一不认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国的超人气女影星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:14:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要问为什么这个女影星能乔装成别人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 以前没和你说过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚出道的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经出演一名女间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能够演好这个角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去向一位著名的日本魔术师拜师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习易容术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗也是为了同样的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个魔术师那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们就成了好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.70,0:14:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我不能像莎朗那样学谁都像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 妈妈那与其说是易容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如说是变装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思啊 我的是变装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是变装 我也是很认真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…疼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好棒 能遇到这样的名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是在纽约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要好好感谢上帝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上真的有上帝吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 那种东西真的存在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.80,0:15:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些拼命努力的人就不会陷入困境了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 即使是一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使也从来没有对我微笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那悲哀的微笑说不定正暗示着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来发生的惨剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不愿回想起来的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那让人讨厌的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么天使从来没有对你微笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是说一直很辛苦的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生只不过是不幸的继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「逝去的思念」公演当天 父母死于火灾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得奥斯卡奖的第二天 丈夫病死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.40,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和作为我的女儿才一出道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被倍受宠爱的克莉丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.20,0:16:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不应该是让你自豪的女儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.70,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的人 我已经不当她是女儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她易容成我丈夫的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我扫墓的时候 站在我的身后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我丈夫一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是玩笑 你不觉得太过分了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 话说回来 莎朗你说过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿死缠着你要学易容术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那孩子也就到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经快十年没见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.90,0:17:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说她最近和一些坏朋友在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.60,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.50,0:17:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该把车停到停车场 去后台了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.30,0:17:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人也开始发现这里没有摄影机了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么一定要在开演前一个小时来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再早一点来的话也不会打扰到他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以轻松的聊天不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再早点来见到的他们也不过是平常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开演前的话 呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 那不是莎朗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员难得也会说真话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.30,0:18:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 好感动 好像做梦一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 一起去吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开演前化了妆才变成了演员呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很崇拜莎朗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.50,0:18:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她和这个剧团的管理员认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说要来看 很容易就拿到票了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.30,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那个人该不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.20,0:18:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 家喻户晓的超人气女侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night Baroness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.80,0:18:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜男爵夫人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 妈妈在这边是被这样称呼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是「暗夜男爵」的作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤优作的妻子咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.20,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈有一次在这里的电视特别节目里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以推理小说家妻子的身份出场过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.10,0:19:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据她那个时候的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快抓到了犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.50,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后就被称作女侦探暗夜男爵夫人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那些推理 也只不过是把爸爸每天早上看报纸时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.20,0:19:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自言自语的推理照样说出来罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人是你的孩子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩的确是 女孩就不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.70,0:19:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说不定以后会是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.70,0:19:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.10,0:19:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 原来以为暗夜男爵夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了解开那个奇怪的包裹之谜而来的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果只是为了来说说笑笑罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的包裹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前这个剧院收到了一个包裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂上了金色颜料的苹果—Golden Apple
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还用动物的血写着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.30,0:20:22.40,Default4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the Fairest
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.30,0:20:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献给最美的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走进后台的时候就觉得气氛有些奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是因为这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 不要慌张 我的女神们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是恶作剧罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个剧场的首席明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西斯·弗洛克哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为决定要出演电影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像是他最后一次出演舞台剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.80,0:20:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 转变一下心情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着莎朗的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我们舞台的内部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离开演只有四十五分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始的二十分钟只不过是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介绍一下这个音乐剧的原身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个希腊神话罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板上的那个是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 舞台服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了节省地方 就吊在了上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.40,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.40,0:21:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.30,0:21:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盔甲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.10,0:21:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不!!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.10,0:23:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.40,0:23:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 小兰拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.50,0:23:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.10,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.10,0:24:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经逃走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.60,0:24:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹壳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.20,0:24:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.50,0:24:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（推理篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.80,0:24:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.70,0:24:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我要开始推理了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.70,0:24:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不好好推理的话还会变小的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.50,0:24:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.80,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:27.57,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,为了两人所说的未来中 能有个地方和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.10,0:00:31.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.87,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,希望变成你的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.57,0:00:43.05,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,相信彼此牵着的手 誓言与你一起迈向前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.16,0:00:49.89,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最讨厌”那种话 即使是谎言也说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.92,0:00:56.94,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,要说是“最喜欢” 如果是谎言我也不会说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.68,0:01:05.11,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就连无法见面的时候 也要让你无暇考虑别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.81,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的心里只有我 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.87,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.02,0:01:24.42,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让两人的爱永不离去 拥抱对方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.24,0:01:31.56,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不安的夜晚总会来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.58,0:01:39.65,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,840)}那时候 请紧紧地将我抱在怀中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.17,0:22:27.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,每个清晨来临的时候都会想起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.55,0:22:33.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在你身旁就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.84,0:22:39.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕因时间的流逝而哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.19,0:22:45.17,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在渐渐改变的人的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.86,0:22:58.76,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有期望也就没有失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.58,0:23:05.55,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,然而不能没有追求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.84,0:23:12.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,无论前方是怎样的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.80,0:23:20.02,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,梦醒以后 你还是那么遥远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.23,0:23:25.55,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是自作多情的徒劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.77,0:23:33.16,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,花雨中的道路还是没有丝毫改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.40,0:23:40.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,880)}真想挽着你的手漫步其中
